```
private <T> Flux<T> monoTofluxUsingFlatMapMany(Mono<List<T>> monoList) {
    return monoList
      .flatMapMany(Flux::fromIterable)
      .log();
}
```

```
private <T> Flux<T> monoTofluxUsingFlatMapIterable(Mono<List<T>> monoList) {
    return monoList
      .flatMapIterable(list -> list)
      .log();
}
